channel.title: Need help with this weird thing when i press run server
channel.description:
[code]Starting TestScape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "5 35 " at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:1031) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:26) at server.main(server.java:26)[/code]
Thats wht i get. GRR wht does it mean and how can i fix?

item.title: Need help with this weird thing when i press run server
item.dc:creator: @I_Br3ndan_I I Br3ndan I
item.description:
@I_Br3ndan_I wrote:

I don’t think you should download another source, that’s terrible advice tbh. Simply re-trace you’re steps, remove anything you’ve added or change back anything that you’ve modified to what it recently was. Then re-add what you wanted to in the first place but be more carefull. It looks like you’ve done something wrong in NPCHandler.CFG imo.
